snippet.title: Secret of Mana (SNES)
snippet.description:
Gameplay video of Secret of Mana for SNES (Super Nintendo). This is from the beginning of the game, including the first boss.  Secret of Mana is an action/RPG that is one of the best games released on the system. (It's in my SNES Top 10). Secret of Mana is now available on the Wii Virtual Console, although this video was made with an actual SNES system.
